119, furca and genital field, posterior; 120, tenaculum; 121, dens, anterior; 122–123, dens, lateral (different specimens); 124, PAO and ocelli; 125, chaetotaxy of Abd.V (s1–4: accp1–4 sensilla); 126, chaetotaxy of lateral part of Th.II (sensilla encircled, s: sensillum, 
<emphasis box="[515,545,1849,1872]" italics="true" pageId="45" pageNumber="46">ms</emphasis>
